00:27:16.320 --> 00:27:19.269
I've done my job. I hope I did it

00:27:19.269 --> 00:27:19.279
well.

00:27:19.279 --> 00:27:21.750
If you're watching,

00:27:21.760 --> 00:27:23.269
Candace,

00:27:23.279 --> 00:27:26.070
God bless you. We pray for you.

00:27:26.080 --> 00:27:27.990
We know that God has a mighty hand on

00:27:28.000 --> 00:27:32.149
you. I pray that you get this fire

00:27:32.159 --> 00:27:34.149
shut up in your bones, the Holy Ghost

00:27:34.159 --> 00:27:36.950
fire. I want you to be radical for

00:27:36.960 --> 00:27:38.950
Jesus. You say, "Well, I'm Catholic; I

00:27:38.960 --> 00:27:39.990
don't care about all that."I'm talking

00:27:40.000 --> 00:27:42.870
about being radical for

00:27:42.870 --> 00:27:42.880
Jesus—fire

00:27:42.880 --> 00:27:46.630
shut up in your bones, the Holy

00:27:46.640 --> 00:27:50.149
Ghost fire, talking in tongues, baptized,

00:27:50.159 --> 00:27:53.190
water walking, laying hands on the

00:27:53.200 --> 00:27:55.110
sick, seeing them recover, casting out

00:27:55.110 --> 00:27:55.120
devils—a

00:27:55.120 --> 00:27:57.750
Christian that the

00:27:57.750 --> 00:27:57.760
devil is

00:27:57.760 --> 00:27:59.990
afraid of when you wake up in

00:27:59.990 --> 00:28:00.000
the

00:28:00.000 --> 00:28:01.990
morning. He goes, "Oh God, she's

00:28:02.000 --> 00:28:04.549
awake again."That's what

00:28:04.559 --> 00:28:07.110
I'm looking for. Not saying, "Well, I go

00:28:07.120 --> 00:28:08.470
and talk to the

00:28:08.470 --> 00:28:08.480
priest."I

00:28:08.480 --> 00:28:11.350
don't care. "I do the

00:28:11.350 --> 00:28:11.360
rosary

00:28:11.360 --> 00:28:12.710
or whatever,"all that stuff. No, I'm

00:28:12.720 --> 00:28:14.549
talking about you talking in tongues. You're

00:28:14.559 --> 00:28:16.549
a fire-breathing Christian and the devil

00:28:16.559 --> 00:28:18.310
goes, "Ah!"when you get up. That's what

00:28:18.320 --> 00:28:20.470
I'm talking about. That's the kind of

00:28:20.480 --> 00:28:22.950
Christian we are. I don't know about

00:28:22.960 --> 00:28:24.549
all that other stuff, talking to popes

00:28:24.559 --> 00:28:26.230
and all that; I don't believe in

00:28:26.240 --> 00:28:28.470
it. I don't stand for it. But

00:28:28.480 --> 00:28:30.230
we believe in

00:28:30.240 --> 00:28:32.310
salvation. We believe in laying

00:28:32.320 --> 00:28:33.590
hands and casting out

00:28:33.590 --> 00:28:33.600
devils.

00:28:33.600 --> 00:28:35.430
It's time to

00:28:35.440 --> 00:28:38.549
get radical for Jesus.

00:28:38.559 --> 00:28:41.029
If we don't get radical for

00:28:41.039 --> 00:28:43.190
Jesus, we're going to lose what we have.

00:28:43.200 --> 00:28:46.710
We must get on fire, for our King is

00:28:46.720 --> 00:28:50.549
coming. We must be the virgins with the

00:28:50.559 --> 00:28:53.830
lamps full of oil. There were ten of them:

00:28:53.840 --> 00:28:56.070
five had their lamps full and five

00:28:56.080 --> 00:28:58.070
didn't. Ladies and gentlemen, which one

00:28:58.080 --> 00:29:00.389
are you?

00:29:00.399 --> 00:29:02.950
Have you lost your saltiness?

00:29:05.360 --> 00:29:07.669
You must remain salty because it is the

00:29:07.679 --> 00:29:11.269
salt that brings men to thirst.

00:29:16.880 --> 00:29:19.430
It's time for you to put on the new

00:29:19.440 --> 00:29:21.830
things and put that new wine in new

00:29:21.830 --> 00:29:21.840
wineskins

00:29:21.840 --> 00:29:24.470
and stop trying to be the old

00:29:24.480 --> 00:29:26.149
person. He said He

00:29:26.159 --> 00:29:28.630
would rather you be hot or cold, but if

00:29:28.640 --> 00:29:30.789
you're lukewarm, He'll spew you out of

00:29:30.799 --> 00:29:34.149
His mouth. How hard is that? But

00:29:34.159 --> 00:29:36.149
yet, we have so many Christians that are

00:29:36.159 --> 00:29:38.950
lukewarm—limp-wristed

00:29:38.960 --> 00:29:41.990
and

00:29:42.000 --> 00:29:44.149
spineless. You don't have a backbone

00:29:44.159 --> 00:29:47.029
like a crowbar Christian.

00:29:47.039 --> 00:29:49.350
It's not always easy to

00:29:49.360 --> 00:29:51.590
stand on this side and tell

00:29:51.600 --> 00:29:53.830
you what I hear, but

00:29:53.840 --> 00:29:56.549
I'll be bold. And if it costs me my

00:29:56.559 --> 00:29:58.630
life, so be it. I believe that His

00:29:58.640 --> 00:30:00.710
angels will bear me up in their hands

00:30:00.720 --> 00:30:02.950
lest I dash my foot against a stone.

00:30:02.960 --> 00:30:05.269
I'll keep declaring it until He calls me

00:30:05.279 --> 00:30:06.950
home.

00:30:06.960 --> 00:30:10.630
Jesus is coming and you need to repent

00:30:10.640 --> 00:30:12.470
and turn from your wicked

00:30:12.480 --> 00:30:14.789
ways or you're going to burn in hell.

00:30:16.480 --> 00:30:19.830
You must know Him.

00:30:19.840 --> 00:30:21.830
If you don't know Jesus Christ as your

00:30:21.840 --> 00:30:23.990
Lord and personal Savior, there's no

00:30:24.000 --> 00:30:25.669
other way to the Father except through

00:30:25.679 --> 00:30:27.269
Him.

00:30:27.279 --> 00:30:29.510
The Holy Spirit is our comforter,

00:30:29.520 --> 00:30:31.909
our friend, and our standby,

00:30:31.919 --> 00:30:34.230
and He prays with me all the time.

00:30:34.240 --> 00:30:35.750
That's what brings

00:30:35.760 --> 00:30:37.830
perfect prayers.

00:30:37.840 --> 00:30:40.149
We must have a relationship with the

00:30:40.159 --> 00:30:44.950
Holy Spirit and be His friend.

00:30:44.960 --> 00:30:46.789
I love how He talks about my friend

00:30:46.799 --> 00:30:49.350
Billy Burke. He always calls

00:30:49.350 --> 00:30:49.360
him,

00:30:49.360 --> 00:30:51.909
"My friend,

00:30:51.919 --> 00:30:55.110
my friend."The Lord says, "Pray for my friend

00:30:55.120 --> 00:30:57.830
today."And

00:30:57.840 --> 00:31:00.389
I say, "You want me to pray for your

00:31:00.399 --> 00:31:02.389
friend today?"He

00:31:02.389 --> 00:31:02.399
doesn't

00:31:02.399 --> 00:31:04.870
do that very often.

00:31:04.880 --> 00:31:07.990
It's alarming to me. He

00:31:07.990 --> 00:31:08.000
doesn't

00:31:08.000 --> 00:31:11.029
call very many people His friend like that. You

00:31:11.039 --> 00:31:12.950
say, "Well, I'm a friend of

00:31:12.960 --> 00:31:17.029
God,"but

00:31:17.039 --> 00:31:18.950
does He call you friend? I'm not trying

00:31:18.960 --> 00:31:22.549
to judge you, but I know when He calls

00:31:22.559 --> 00:31:24.789
people His friend. He'll say, "Brandon,

00:31:24.799 --> 00:31:29.430
will you pray for my friend

00:31:29.440 --> 00:31:32.230
today?"Of

00:31:32.240 --> 00:31:37.110
course I will. Who? Billy.

00:31:37.120 --> 00:31:41.350
Okay.

00:31:41.360 --> 00:31:42.789
But He doesn't do that very often, does

00:31:42.799 --> 00:31:45.029
He?

00:31:46.320 --> 00:31:48.470
He'll

00:31:48.480 --> 00:31:49.990
say certain people by

00:31:50.000 --> 00:31:52.389
their name, but very rarely will He ever

00:31:52.389 --> 00:31:52.399
say,

00:31:52.399 --> 00:31:55.750
"Will you pray for my

00:31:55.750 --> 00:31:55.760
friend?"I

00:31:55.760 --> 00:31:57.830
thought, "What does it take for You

00:31:57.840 --> 00:32:00.710
to call my name to somebody and say, 'Will

00:32:00.720 --> 00:32:05.110
you pray for my friend

00:32:05.110 --> 00:32:05.120
Brandon?'"I'm

00:32:05.120 --> 00:32:09.190
challenged by it. I'm jealous

00:32:09.200 --> 00:32:11.269
of their relationship because

00:32:11.269 --> 00:32:11.279
I think,

00:32:11.279 --> 00:32:14.389
"Man, if He calls him friend

00:32:14.399 --> 00:32:17.509
to me privately, what does He call me to

00:32:17.519 --> 00:32:19.029
him?""Am

00:32:19.039 --> 00:32:21.590
I your friend?

00:32:21.600 --> 00:32:24.630
I want to be your friend so

00:32:24.630 --> 00:32:24.640
bad."Not

00:32:24.640 --> 00:32:29.750
just a relationship of acquaintance,

00:32:29.760 --> 00:32:33.430
but intimacy with the Father. There

00:32:33.430 --> 00:32:33.440
are

00:32:33.440 --> 00:32:36.630
so many people that are just

00:32:36.640 --> 00:32:39.350
visitors

00:32:39.360 --> 00:32:41.350
when it comes to

00:32:41.360 --> 00:32:44.870
the relationship with the Lord. I tell

00:32:44.880 --> 00:32:46.950
Diana all the time—we talk about

00:32:46.950 --> 00:32:46.960
it—we

00:32:46.960 --> 00:32:49.830
must be friends with Him.

00:32:51.600 --> 00:32:53.909
Diana and I don't

00:32:53.919 --> 00:32:55.509
keep anything from each other; we

00:32:55.519 --> 00:32:58.389
talk about everything.

00:32:58.399 --> 00:33:01.350
I don't say this arrogantly,

00:33:01.350 --> 00:33:01.360
but

00:33:01.360 --> 00:33:02.710
I don't know many

00:33:02.720 --> 00:33:05.190
relationships like ours. We spend 24

00:33:05.200 --> 00:33:06.549
hours a day, seven days a week with each

00:33:06.559 --> 00:33:09.830
other, and we very seldom bicker.

00:33:09.840 --> 00:33:11.830
We have our stuff we go through, but

00:33:11.840 --> 00:33:15.909
she's my friend.

00:33:15.919 --> 00:33:20.310
I thought about when the Lord

00:33:20.320 --> 00:33:24.230
calls us to Him, what

00:33:24.240 --> 00:33:29.430
does He say about you to others?

00:33:29.440 --> 00:33:31.110
I heard a preacher say

00:33:31.120 --> 00:33:34.710
before,

00:33:39.200 --> 00:33:41.190
"Man, that person has anger.

00:33:41.200 --> 00:33:43.909
He's full of

00:33:43.909 --> 00:33:43.919
evil."Evil

00:33:43.919 --> 00:33:46.389
has a

00:33:46.399 --> 00:33:49.029
presence.

00:33:49.039 --> 00:33:51.990
Lust has a presence.

00:33:52.000 --> 00:33:55.430
Anger has a presence.

00:33:55.440 --> 00:34:01.669
Child pedophiles have a presence.

00:34:01.679 --> 00:34:03.669
But when you get around somebody,

00:34:03.679 --> 00:34:05.750
what presence

00:34:05.760 --> 00:34:09.030
do you carry? How much do you carry?

00:34:09.040 --> 00:34:12.149
What are you full of? I

00:34:12.159 --> 00:34:13.589
thought about that a lot because I heard Billy

00:34:13.589 --> 00:34:13.599
Graham

00:34:13.599 --> 00:34:17.270
preach that. Billy,

00:34:17.280 --> 00:34:19.030
I was thinking,

00:34:19.040 --> 00:34:21.109
what does the Father say about

00:34:21.119 --> 00:34:24.869
you?

00:34:24.879 --> 00:34:26.790
Does He call you friend? You call Him

00:34:26.800 --> 00:34:28.389
friend: "Oh yeah, He's my

00:34:28.389 --> 00:34:28.399
friend."But

00:34:28.399 --> 00:34:30.470
does He call

00:34:30.480 --> 00:34:32.950
you friend?

00:34:32.960 --> 00:34:37.909
I want it so bad.

00:34:37.919 --> 00:34:41.190
It's not just the

00:34:41.200 --> 00:34:44.230
glory,

00:34:44.240 --> 00:34:46.069
but it's the

00:34:46.079 --> 00:34:48.869
anointing that breaks the yoke. You can

00:34:48.879 --> 00:34:50.389
have the glory

00:34:50.389 --> 00:34:50.399
filling

00:34:50.399 --> 00:34:51.909
the house, but I thought, "Where is the

00:34:51.919 --> 00:34:53.510
anointing that

00:34:53.520 --> 00:34:55.349
breaks the

00:34:55.349 --> 00:34:55.359
yoke?"It's

00:34:55.359 --> 00:34:57.430
a tool that helps set

00:34:57.440 --> 00:35:00.390
the captives free. It comes in

00:35:00.400 --> 00:35:03.589
stages and levels—ankle-deep, knee-deep, waist-deep, and over-the-head deep. There are levels

00:35:11.040 --> 00:35:12.790
of the glory and levels of

00:35:12.800 --> 00:35:14.470
the anointing, and it all comes by

00:35:14.480 --> 00:35:18.470
refining fire and dying

00:35:18.480 --> 00:35:21.109
to self.

00:35:21.119 --> 00:35:23.750
How much of you does He have?

00:35:30.880 --> 00:35:32.630
It's not so much how much you

00:35:32.640 --> 00:35:33.910
have of Him, but how much He

00:35:33.910 --> 00:35:33.920
has of

00:35:33.920 --> 00:35:36.310
you. I

00:35:36.310 --> 00:35:36.320
am wall-to-wall

00:35:36.320 --> 00:35:38.950
Holy Ghost, but

00:35:38.960 --> 00:35:41.750
does He have

00:35:44.000 --> 00:35:46.870
all of me? Am I crucified with Christ?

00:35:46.870 --> 00:35:46.880
Nevertheless,

00:35:46.880 --> 00:35:48.470
I, but Christ in me, the hope

00:35:48.480 --> 00:35:49.990
of glory.

00:35:50.000 --> 00:35:51.750
That's why I try to tell you all this

00:35:51.760 --> 00:35:53.510
other stuff, the Candace stuff. I

00:35:53.520 --> 00:35:55.589
feel like it's a big distraction today.

00:35:55.599 --> 00:35:59.430
It pulls me and it caused me peace

00:35:59.440 --> 00:36:02.390
because I'm like, "Oh man, what did I

00:36:02.390 --> 00:36:02.400
do?"And

00:36:02.400 --> 00:36:04.550
the Lord said, "You did me a

00:36:04.560 --> 00:36:07.670
favor

00:36:07.680 --> 00:36:10.870
today."I

00:36:10.880 --> 00:36:13.030
was cleaning out my

00:36:13.040 --> 00:36:15.750
freezer, getting the ice out,

00:36:15.750 --> 00:36:15.760
and

00:36:15.760 --> 00:36:18.790
I said, "Lord,

00:36:18.800 --> 00:36:20.870
what did I do? What did I

00:36:20.870 --> 00:36:20.880
say?"And

00:36:20.880 --> 00:36:23.430
He said,

00:36:32.800 --> 00:36:34.870
"You're helping me because I

00:36:34.880 --> 00:36:37.510
want Candace.

00:36:37.520 --> 00:36:39.349
I want more of

00:36:39.359 --> 00:36:41.190
Candace,

00:36:41.200 --> 00:36:47.589
for I have a plan for

00:36:47.589 --> 00:36:47.599
her."I

00:36:47.599 --> 00:36:51.109
said, "Okay,

00:36:51.119 --> 00:36:55.990
whatever I can do to help you,

00:37:01.510 --> 00:37:01.520
Father."It's

00:37:06.480 --> 00:37:09.030
such an honor that 5,100

00:37:09.040 --> 00:37:11.670
of you are here tonight to

00:37:11.680 --> 00:37:13.190
pray for our nation and

00:37:15.680 --> 00:37:17.430
this beautiful

00:37:17.440 --> 00:37:19.270
Thanksgiving season where we give God

00:37:19.280 --> 00:37:21.510
thanks and praise for a free

00:37:21.520 --> 00:37:25.030
nation that's one nation under God.

00:37:25.040 --> 00:37:27.829
I'm not

00:37:27.839 --> 00:37:31.270
here to judge a man's heart like

00:37:31.280 --> 00:37:33.829
JD Vance; I pray that he gets

00:37:33.839 --> 00:37:37.190
even more radical

00:37:37.190 --> 00:37:37.200
for Jesus.

00:37:37.200 --> 00:37:41.109
I only relay what I believe I

00:37:41.119 --> 00:37:46.230
heard the Lord

00:37:46.230 --> 00:37:46.240
say—that

00:37:46.240 --> 00:37:50.069
He wants more of him.

00:37:50.079 --> 00:37:52.550
The whole Harvard thing

00:37:56.640 --> 00:37:58.950
was rooted in a mindset. Ivy

00:37:58.960 --> 00:38:01.990
League colleges will poison you.

00:38:05.440 --> 00:38:09.030
Regardless of if you

00:38:09.040 --> 00:38:11.030
graduated there and are standing on

00:38:11.040 --> 00:38:16.230
the right, the left is teaching you.

00:38:23.119 --> 00:38:25.190
That's why I really

00:38:25.200 --> 00:38:27.109
believe in ORU

00:38:27.119 --> 00:38:29.589
and colleges that

00:38:29.599 --> 00:38:31.670
have a

00:38:32.400 --> 00:38:37.589
biblical-based Christian school.

00:38:37.599 --> 00:38:45.270
Don't feed your kids to the wolves.

00:38:45.280 --> 00:38:47.030
It gets in you regardless of whether you think

00:38:47.040 --> 00:38:51.190
it does or not.

00:38:51.200 --> 00:38:53.109
It's a little leaven that ruins the

00:38:53.119 --> 00:38:56.470
whole lump. Remember,

00:38:56.480 --> 00:38:58.710
a little leaven ruins the whole lump. I

00:38:58.720 --> 00:39:02.630
just want to be on fire for Jesus,

00:39:02.640 --> 00:39:05.270
and that's why we're here tonight. So,

00:39:05.280 --> 00:39:07.030
with all that being said, who wants to

00:39:07.040 --> 00:39:09.270
go tubing? You want to pray with us for

00:39:09.280 --> 00:39:13.430
a little bit? I talked for 40

00:39:13.430 --> 00:39:13.440
minutes—not

00:39:13.440 --> 00:39:15.510
too bad. I hope

00:39:15.510 --> 00:39:15.520
I cleared

00:39:15.520 --> 00:39:18.150
it up

00:39:18.160 --> 00:39:20.710
and

00:39:20.720 --> 00:39:25.190
made peace in your heart.

00:39:25.200 --> 00:39:28.230
I touched as much as I could.

00:39:34.480 --> 00:39:38.950
Father, I thank You

00:39:38.960 --> 00:39:42.230
for how good You've been to us.

00:39:42.240 --> 00:39:44.630
Even if we

00:39:44.640 --> 00:39:48.630
miss it, there's grace to cover it.

00:39:48.640 --> 00:39:49.990
We're all

00:39:50.000 --> 00:39:51.589
human; none of us are Jesus Christ. We

00:39:51.589 --> 00:39:51.599
are

00:39:51.599 --> 00:39:55.030
all striving to be just like

00:39:57.520 --> 00:39:59.750
the King.

00:39:59.760 --> 00:40:04.230
We

00:40:08.880 --> 00:40:12.230
all

00:40:16.800 --> 00:40:19.349
come short of the glory,

00:40:19.359 --> 00:40:21.750
but it's by His grace and mercy that we

00:40:21.750 --> 00:40:21.760
are

00:40:21.760 --> 00:40:24.550
set free. When you fall down,

00:40:24.560 --> 00:40:26.870
you pick yourself up,

00:40:26.880 --> 00:40:28.390
brush your knees off, and keep

00:40:28.400 --> 00:40:32.069
marching.

00:40:36.480 --> 00:40:39.030
Be humble

00:40:39.040 --> 00:40:41.910
and say, "Lord, tomorrow's a better

00:40:49.119 --> 00:40:51.030
day."It's

00:40:56.319 --> 00:40:59.430
so

00:40:59.440 --> 00:41:01.349
heavy on me to pray for

00:41:01.359 --> 00:41:04.550
Candace

00:41:04.560 --> 00:41:07.670
because the

00:41:07.680 --> 00:41:10.550
rabbit hole is very bad.

00:41:10.560 --> 00:41:13.430
There's much truth to

00:41:13.440 --> 00:41:15.430
the rabbit hole, but

00:41:15.430 --> 00:41:15.440
it

00:41:15.440 --> 00:41:18.630
has a snare.

00:41:20.513 --> 00:41:23.109
There

00:41:25.440 --> 00:41:27.430
are

00:41:29.520 --> 00:41:31.670
levels of what you

00:41:31.680 --> 00:41:33.510
should touch for

00:41:33.510 --> 00:41:33.520
the

00:41:33.520 --> 00:41:35.349
safety of your own family.

00:41:39.599 --> 00:41:43.428
I say what I feel I'm called to say.

00:41:47.200 --> 00:41:48.790
God help us all.

